#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:1
msgid "Knowledge (`lu_mcp_knowledge`)"
msgstr "Knowledge (`lu_mcp_knowledge`)"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:3
msgid "**9 tools** for Odoo Knowledge article CRUD."
msgstr "Odoo Knowledge 아티클 CRUD를 위한 **9가지 도구**입니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:5
msgid "Requires: `lu_mcp_server`, Odoo `knowledge` app."
msgstr "필요 조건: `lu_mcp_server`, Odoo `knowledge` 앱."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:9
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "개요"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:11
msgid ""
"These tools let an AI client browse the Knowledge article hierarchy, read"
" and search articles, and create, update, move, or soft-delete articles. "
"Article bodies are exchanged as Markdown — the plugin converts to/from "
"Odoo HTML automatically."
msgstr "이 도구들은 AI 클라이언트가 Knowledge 아티클 계층을 탐색하고, 아티클을 읽고 검색하며, 생성·업데이트·이동·소프트 삭제할 수 있도록 합니다. 아티클 본문은 Markdown으로 교환되며, 플러그인이 Odoo HTML과 자동으로 변환합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:17
msgid "Tools"
msgstr "도구"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:19
msgid "`knowledge_list_workspaces`"
msgstr "`knowledge_list_workspaces`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:21
msgid "List all top-level workspace articles."
msgstr "모든 최상위 워크스페이스 아티클을 나열합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "Parameter"
msgstr "파라미터"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "Type"
msgstr "유형"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "Required"
msgstr "필수"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "Description"
msgstr "설명"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md
msgid "*(none)*"
msgstr "*(없음)*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:27 ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:41
#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:54 ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:68
#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:82 ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:98
#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:177 ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:190
msgid "**Example prompt**"
msgstr "**예제 프롬프트**"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:28
msgid "*\"Show me all Knowledge workspaces.\"*"
msgstr "*\"모든 Knowledge 워크스페이스를 보여주세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:32
msgid "`knowledge_list_articles`"
msgstr "`knowledge_list_articles`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:34
msgid "List direct children of a parent article, or root articles of a category."
msgstr "부모 아티클의 직접 하위 아티클 또는 카테고리의 루트 아티클을 나열합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "`parent_id`"
msgstr "`parent_id`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "integer"
msgstr "integer"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "No"
msgstr "아니요"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md
msgid "ID of the parent article. Omit to list root articles."
msgstr "부모 아티클의 ID. 루트 아티클을 나열하려면 생략하세요."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "`category`"
msgstr "`category`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "string"
msgstr "string"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md
msgid "`workspace`, `private`, or `shared`. Used when `parent_id` is omitted."
msgstr "`workspace`, `private`, `shared` 중 하나. `parent_id`가 생략되었을 때 사용됩니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:42
msgid "*\"List the articles inside the HR Policies workspace (id=42).\"*"
msgstr "*\"HR Policies 워크스페이스(id=42) 내의 아티클을 나열하세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:46
msgid "`knowledge_read_article`"
msgstr "`knowledge_read_article`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:48
msgid ""
"Read the full content (title + body) of an article. Body is returned as "
"Markdown."
msgstr "아티클의 전체 내용(제목 + 본문)을 읽습니다. 본문은 Markdown으로 반환됩니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "`article_id`"
msgstr "`article_id`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "예"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md
msgid "Numeric ID of the article to read."
msgstr "읽을 아티클의 숫자 ID."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:55
msgid "*\"Read Knowledge article #105.\"*"
msgstr "*\"Knowledge 아티클 #105를 읽으세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:59
msgid "`knowledge_search_articles`"
msgstr "`knowledge_search_articles`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:61
msgid "Search articles by keyword. Searches both title and body content."
msgstr "키워드로 아티클을 검색합니다. 제목과 본문 내용 모두에서 검색합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md
msgid "`query`"
msgstr "`query`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md
msgid "Search keyword or phrase."
msgstr "검색 키워드 또는 문구."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md
msgid "`limit`"
msgstr "`limit`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md
msgid "Maximum results (default 20, max 80)."
msgstr "최대 결과 수(기본값 20, 최대 80)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:69
msgid "*\"Find Knowledge articles about 'onboarding'.\"*"
msgstr "*\"'온보딩'에 관한 Knowledge 아티클을 찾으세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:73
msgid "`knowledge_get_article_tree`"
msgstr "`knowledge_get_article_tree`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:75
msgid "Show the article hierarchy tree starting from a given article."
msgstr "지정된 아티클에서 시작하는 아티클 계층 트리를 표시합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md
msgid "Root article ID for the tree view."
msgstr "트리 뷰의 루트 아티클 ID."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md
msgid "`depth`"
msgstr "`depth`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md
msgid "How many levels to expand (1–4, default 2)."
msgstr "확장할 레벨 수(1~4, 기본값 2)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:83
msgid "*\"Show the article tree under workspace #10, 3 levels deep.\"*"
msgstr "*\"워크스페이스 #10 아래의 아티클 트리를 3단계까지 표시하세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:87
msgid "`knowledge_create_article`"
msgstr "`knowledge_create_article`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:89
msgid "Create a new Knowledge article."
msgstr "새 Knowledge 아티클을 생성합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "`name`"
msgstr "`name`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md
msgid "Article title."
msgstr "아티클 제목."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "`body_markdown`"
msgstr "`body_markdown`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md
msgid "Article body in Markdown."
msgstr "Markdown 형식의 아티클 본문."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md
msgid "Parent article ID. Omit to create a private article."
msgstr "부모 아티클 ID. 비공개 아티클을 생성하려면 생략하세요."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "`icon`"
msgstr "`icon`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md
msgid "Emoji icon (e.g. `📝`)."
msgstr "이모지 아이콘(예: `📝`)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:99
msgid ""
"*\"Create a Knowledge article titled 'Q3 OKRs' under workspace #10 with "
"the following content: ...\"*"
msgstr "*\"워크스페이스 #10 아래에 'Q3 OKRs'라는 제목의 Knowledge 아티클을 다음 내용으로 생성하세요: ...\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:102
msgid ""
"Articles created without a `parent_id` are placed in the **private** "
"category. To create a workspace article, supply the workspace article's "
"ID as `parent_id`."
msgstr "`parent_id` 없이 생성한 아티클은 **비공개** 카테고리에 배치됩니다. 워크스페이스 아티클을 생성하려면 워크스페이스 아티클의 ID를 `parent_id`로 지정하세요."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:108
msgid "`knowledge_update_article`"
msgstr "`knowledge_update_article`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:110
msgid ""
"Update an existing article. Use `body_markdown` to replace the entire "
"body, or `content_updates` for partial edits. The two are mutually "
"exclusive."
msgstr "기존 아티클을 업데이트합니다. `body_markdown`을 사용하여 본문 전체를 교체하거나 `content_updates`로 부분 편집할 수 있습니다. 둘은 상호 배타적입니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "ID of the article to update."
msgstr "업데이트할 아티클의 ID."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "New title. Omit to keep existing."
msgstr "새 제목. 기존 제목을 유지하려면 생략하세요."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "Replace the entire body with this Markdown."
msgstr "본문 전체를 이 Markdown으로 교체합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "`content_updates`"
msgstr "`content_updates`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "array"
msgstr "array"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "List of partial update operations (see below)."
msgstr "부분 업데이트 작업 목록(아래 참조)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "New emoji icon."
msgstr "새 이모지 아이콘."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:121
msgid "**`content_updates` operations**"
msgstr "**`content_updates` 작업**"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:123
msgid "Each item is an object with:"
msgstr "각 항목은 다음과 같은 객체입니다:"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "Field"
msgstr "필드"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "Values"
msgstr "값"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "`type`"
msgstr "`type`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "`append`"
msgstr "`append`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "Add content at the end of the article."
msgstr "아티클 끝에 내용을 추가합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "`prepend`"
msgstr "`prepend`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "Add content at the beginning."
msgstr "시작 부분에 내용을 추가합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "`replace_section`"
msgstr "`replace_section`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "Replace a named Markdown section heading and its content."
msgstr "지정된 Markdown 섹션 제목과 해당 내용을 교체합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "`insert_after`"
msgstr "`insert_after`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "Insert content after a named Markdown section heading."
msgstr "지정된 Markdown 섹션 제목 다음에 내용을 삽입합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "`content`"
msgstr "`content`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "Markdown text to insert or replace with."
msgstr "삽입하거나 교체할 Markdown 텍스트."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "`target`"
msgstr "`target`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid ""
"Required for `replace_section` and `insert_after`. The exact section "
"heading text."
msgstr "`replace_section`과 `insert_after`에 필수. 정확한 섹션 제목 텍스트."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:134
msgid "**Example prompt — append**"
msgstr "**예제 프롬프트 — 추가**"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:135
msgid ""
"*\"Append a new section '## Action Items' with a task list to article "
"#105.\"*"
msgstr "*\"아티클 #105에 작업 목록이 있는 '## Action Items' 섹션을 추가하세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:149
msgid "**Example prompt — replace section**"
msgstr "**예제 프롬프트 — 섹션 교체**"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:150
msgid "*\"Replace the 'Status' section in article #105 with 'Completed'.\"*"
msgstr "*\"아티클 #105의 'Status' 섹션을 'Completed'로 교체하세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:167
msgid "`knowledge_move_article`"
msgstr "`knowledge_move_article`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:169
msgid "Move an article to a different location in the Knowledge hierarchy."
msgstr "아티클을 Knowledge 계층의 다른 위치로 이동합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "ID of the article to move."
msgstr "이동할 아티클의 ID."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "New parent article ID. Omit to move to the workspace root."
msgstr "새 부모 아티클 ID. 워크스페이스 루트로 이동하려면 생략하세요."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid ""
"Target category: `workspace`, `private`, or `shared` (default "
"`workspace`)."
msgstr "대상 카테고리: `workspace`, `private`, `shared` 중 하나(기본값 `workspace`)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:178
msgid "*\"Move article #88 to the root of the workspace.\"*"
msgstr "*\"아티클 #88을 워크스페이스의 루트로 이동하세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:182
msgid "`knowledge_delete_article`"
msgstr "`knowledge_delete_article`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:184
msgid ""
"Send an article to trash (soft delete). Trashed articles can be recovered"
" within 30 days."
msgstr "아티클을 휴지통으로 이동합니다(소프트 삭제). 삭제된 아티클은 30일 이내에 복구할 수 있습니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:101
msgid "ID of the article to trash."
msgstr "휴지통으로 이동할 아티클의 ID."

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:191
msgid "*\"Delete Knowledge article #88.\"*"
msgstr "*\"Knowledge 아티클 #88을 삭제하세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/knowledge.md:194
msgid ""
"`knowledge_delete_article` performs a **soft delete** (moves to trash). "
"The article is recoverable from the Odoo Knowledge trash for up to 30 "
"days. This is not a permanent deletion."
msgstr "`knowledge_delete_article`은 **소프트 삭제**(휴지통으로 이동)를 수행합니다. 아티클은 Odoo Knowledge 휴지통에서 최대 30일 이내에 복구할 수 있습니다. 영구 삭제가 아닙니다."
